This paper discusses the security of storage stack on smart devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a novel architecture for storage stack, which involves outsourcing file system logic and metadata to the cloud, which falls under the categories of operating systems (cs.OS) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the challenges of implementing this architecture, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed systems (cs.DS).
